%% V1.0.13
%% Overview Feed

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as App/Consumer
    participant getOverview as getOverview
    participant VideoAPI as Video API
    participant ChannelAPI as Channel API

    App->>getOverview: getOverview(VIDEO_API_URL, CHANNEL_API_URL, ...)

    par Parallel fetch
        getOverview->>VideoAPI: GET all videos
        VideoAPI-->>getOverview: videos
    and
        getOverview->>ChannelAPI: GET all channels
        ChannelAPI-->>getOverview: channels
    end

    getOverview->>getOverview: Build thumbnailMap, channelLogoMap
    getOverview->>getOverview: Enrich videos (thumbnailUrl, channelLogoUrl, videoTimeAgo)
    getOverview->>getOverview: Merge featured video, format response

    getOverview-->>App: { data: { videos, featuredVideo } }